--*
--* CLASSES: FINITE_ORDERED_PARTIAL(K,T1,T2) 
--* 
--* IMPLEMENTATION OF: 
--*
--* CONFORMS TO: FINITE_ORDERED(T) FINITE_PARTIAL(K,T) ORDERED_PARTIAL(K,T)
--*
--* IS A: 
--*
--* REQUIRED CLASSES: ORDERED(T) FINITE_ORDERED(T) FINITE_PARTIAL(K,T) ORDERED_PARTIAL(K,T)
--*
--* EXCEPTIONS: 
--*
--* TEST CLASS: 
--*
--* FOREIGN FILES:
--*
